You wish to enable the Native Execution Engine for a specific notebook to speed up queries on Parquet files. You add the following configuration cell at the top of your notebook:

```json
%%configure
{
    "conf": {
        "spark.native.enabled": "true",
        "spark.shuffle.manager": "org.apache.spark.shuffle.sort.ColumnarShuffleManager"
    }
}
```

What is the primary technical benefit of adding this code?
